songs.title: Disintegrate Me
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Disintegrate me over and over again
‘Cause all I need is love and adrenaline
All I need is you
All I need is you

Disintegrate me over and over again
‘Cause all I want is love from an alien
All I need is you
All I need is you

[Chorus]
But it’s too late and you can’t stay
So baby… Say what you say and be on your way
Say what you say and be on your way

[Verse 2]
I knew a girl
Her name was Elizabeth
And she grew up to live in the thick of it
And she just need you…
I think she still needs you…

[Chorus]
But it’s too late and you can’t stay
So baby… Say what you say and be on your way
Say what you say and be on your way

[Outro]
Now it’s too late and you can’t stay
So baby… Say what you say and be on your way
Say what you say and be on your way
‘Cause it’s too late and you can’t stay
So baby… Say what you say and be on your way
Say what you say and be on your way
